{{Vgname|荒野星球|en=WildStar}}，或譯'''狂野之星'''，是一個[[奇幻|奇幻]]/[[科幻|科幻]]類[[大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲|大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲]]，設定在行星納克瑟斯（Nexus）上。在這座星球上強大的迷之種族Eldan消失之後留下了大量供玩家探索的技藝與秘密。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fahey|first=Mike|url=http://kotaku.com/5831906/im-falling-in-love-with-wildstar-and-i-dont-care-who-knows-it/|title=I'm Falling in Love With WildStar, and I Don't Care Who Knows It|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=August 17, 2011|accessdate=June 18, 2013|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231084921/http://kotaku.com/5831906/im-falling-in-love-with-wildstar-and-i-dont-care-who-knows-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Brendan|last=Caldwell|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/05/30/viewed-prior-to-release-wildstar/|title=Viewed Prior To Release: Wildstar|work=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|date=May 30, 2013|accessdate=June 18, 2013|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231085245/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/05/30/viewed-prior-to-release-wildstar/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

《荒野星球》的開發商是[[Carbine_Studios|Carbine Studios]]，由[[NCSOFT|NCSOFT]]發行，在2011年8月17日於[[Gamescom|Gamescom]]上首次露面。<ref name="Reveal">{{cite web|url=http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/08/17/ncsoft-announces-new-mmo-wildstar/|title=NCsoft announces new MMO: WildStar|publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]|date=August 17, 2011|accessdate=June 18, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110230225/http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/08/17/ncsoft-announces-new-mmo-wildstar/|archive-date=2015-01-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2014年6月3日上線。在首次購買之後，這款遊戲給玩家提供了兩種付款方法，一種是月付，一種是購買遊戲內的C.R.E.D.D，後者可在遊戲中交易。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gaffney|first=Jeremy|url=http://www.wildstar-online.com/en/news/the_business_model_of_wildstar.php|title=The Business Model of WildStar|work=WildStar-Online|date=August 19, 2013|accessdate=August 19, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822012339/http://www.wildstar-online.com/en/news/the_business_model_of_wildstar.php|archivedate=2013-08-22}}</ref>

